<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人开始介绍自己：“我是法达王子，这是花仙子王国。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他开始吹口哨，所有的花朵都陆续开放了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一朵花里都有像拇指姑娘一样大的小人在里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都朝她微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里可能是我真正的家。”她自言自语说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘见到跟她一样大的人，心里又惊又喜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫拇指姑娘。”她说，“你们住在花朵里面吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，每一朵花都是一个家。”王子笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的家在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道，法达王子。”拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只知道我喜欢做什么，比如说看星星。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们坐在花朵里面，仰望夜晚的星空。”王子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后我们一起唱歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还记得玛丽戈尔德夫人的窗台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你住在什么花里？”王子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的床是铺着郁金香被子的胡桃壳儿。”拇指姑娘回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，郁金香，我们最喜欢的花。”法达王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很激动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请告诉我你是怎么找到我们的。”王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘就把发生的一切都告诉了王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们也喜欢冒险。”王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是唱歌让我充满力量，也让我开心。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>法达王子的眼睛亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们都有着美妙的嗓音，也爱唱歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我发现我可以很快地学会鸟儿的歌曲。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们和鸟是很好的朋友。”法达王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿他又说：“你看起来像我们，听起来也像我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是有一件事情我跟你们不一样。”拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有翅膀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>法达王子微笑着说道：“不，你有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吹了一个欢乐的口哨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个花仙子带来了一双翅膀，她把翅膀安在拇指姑娘身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好漂亮的翅膀！”拇指姑娘激动地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不敢相信自己的眼睛。她害羞地朝王子微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很适合你。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘回头看自己的翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我可以去任何想去的地方了！”她开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子皱了皱眉：“你不想跟我在一起吗？你可以做我的公主。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以幸福地生活在一起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看了看他，然后抬头看了看天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“以前，我不知道自己属于哪里。”她说，“现在，我知道了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我还是想再见到玛丽戈尔德夫人。之后我还想看看整个世界！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“之后我就会开心地回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，王子，我一定会回来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘展开翅膀，飞向天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为拇指姑娘的冒险结束了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是作为花仙子的人生旅途才刚刚开始。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text></Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>